<h2>About</h2>
<p>The app was programmed as part of Machine Learning I course, Data Science and Engineering grade at the <a href="http://www.datascience.es">Data Science Lab.</a> of the University Rey Juan Carlos.</p>
<p>This application is governed by the <a href="http://www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl-3.0"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=utf-8;base64," alt="License: GPL v3" /></a></p>
<p>You can use, modify and/or redistribute these codes under the terms of the GPL v3 license This Shiny application requires the following packages:</p>
<ul>
<li>Shiny, <span class="citation">Chang et al. (2018)</span></li>
<li>dplyr, <span class="citation">Wickham et al. (2018)</span></li>
<li>ggplot, <span class="citation">Wickham (2016)</span>,</li>
<li>shinydashboard, <span class="citation">Chang and Borges Ribeiro (2018)</span></li>
</ul>
<p>Some elements from the app build by <span class="citation">Lavielle (April 29th, 2015)</span> were used.</p>
